---

---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-900 via-brand-800 to-brand-900">
  <!-- Subtle decorative glow -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-brand-500/8 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-brand-700/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative container-narrow mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32 lg:py-40 text-center">
    <!-- Main headline -->
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight animate-fade-in">
      有些话，不知道该跟谁说。
    </h1>

    <!-- Subheadline -->
    <p class="mt-6 md:mt-8 text-base md:text-lg text-brand-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.15s;">
      「问情播客 AskingLove」是一档关于爱情、关系与情绪的中文播客。<br class="hidden md:inline" />
      这里聊心动、失望、拉扯，也聊那些你不知道该跟谁说的话。
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="mt-10 md:mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
      <a href="/listen" class="btn-primary text-base px-10 py-3.5">
        开始收听
      </a>
      <a href="/submit" class="btn-outline-light text-base px-10 py-3.5">
        投稿你的故事
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
